ُلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiliY~N","text_ar":"حِلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, because of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuliY~N","text_ar":"حُلِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSiY~N","text_ar":"عِصِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a pl. [or coll. gen. n.], and its sing. [or n. un.] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloyapN","text_ar":"حَلْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) so says AAF: (TA:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloyapN","text_ar":"حِلْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K; [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuliY~","text_ar":"حُلِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) and particularly, (K,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornaments,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziynapN","text_ar":"زِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh and Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of gold"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silver,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) of a sword, (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalaApN","text_ar":"حَلَاةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or of a lamp, and of other things: (Mgh:) accord. to Lth,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaloYN","text_ar":"حَلْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hiloyap","text_ar":"حِلْيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ornaments,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one decks a woman"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sword and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but accord. to others, only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a woman;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and one says only ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloyapN","text_ar":"حِلْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to other things, to a sword [for instance], and the like: (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiloyapN","text_ar":"حِلْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HilFY","text_ar":"حِلًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HulFY","text_ar":"حُلًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) or, accord. to IF, it has no pl. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n8975","headword_ar":"حَلِى","root":"HlY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cry by which a she-camel is chidden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hali","text_ar":"حَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halo","text_ar":"حَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like as a he-camel is by the cry"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawobi","text_ar":"حَوْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawobu","text_ar":"حَوْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawobi","text_ar":"حَوْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which female camels are chidden;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halo","text_ar":"حَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and, when in connexion with a following word,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalK","text_ar":"حَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halo","text_ar":"حَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hl","text_ar":"حل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says, in chiding the she-camel, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaliY laA Haliyti","text_ar":"حَلِى لَا حَلِيتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"On! mayest thou not gain any great benefit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as one says, in chiding the he-camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Habo","text_ar":"حَبْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA ma$iyta","text_ar":"لَا مَشِيتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.]. (TA in the present art.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n8979","headword_ar":"حَلِىٌّ","root":"HlY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dry, dried up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tough."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What has become dry"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and white"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~N","text_ar":"نَصِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plant called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaT","text_ar":"سَبَط"},{"kind":"text","text":": Az says,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is one of the best kinds of pasture of the people of the desert for camels and horses; and when its produce appears, it resembles eared corn:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Lth, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"every plant that resembles corn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seed-produce, in its manner of growth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this, says Az, is a mistake: (TA:) n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoliyapN","text_ar":"اَحْلِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a plough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is between the two bulls:"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the dial. of El Yemen. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]}]}}